# SEO

## Page metadata

Export `metadata` from every page:

```tsx
export const metadata: Metadata = {
  title: "Page Title | Anna M Schneider Law",
  description: "Descriptive summary for search engines.",
}
```

Title template: `%s | Anna M Schneider Law`

## Structured data

Schema.org JSON-LD via `StructuredData` in layout. Include LocalBusiness, Attorney, and Review schemas where relevant.

## Required files

- `robots.ts` — crawl control
- `sitemap.ts` — add new routes here
- `opengraph-image.tsx` — social previews

## Environment

Set `NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL` in production (sitemap, OG images, structured data).
